2024-08-14 12:48:01 - StudioAtrium\Entity\Discuss\Post:Insert {"timestamp":1723639681,"user_id":null,"user_ip":"62.133.150.195","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit\/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome\/127.0.0.0 Safari\/537.36","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post","entity_data":{"id":10114,"__foreign_props":[],"parent_id":"9539","cat_id":"100","project_id":"1549","nick":"Joanna","topic":"Odp.","content":"Dzie\u0144 dobry. Czy r\u00f3wnie\u017c mog\u0119 prosi\u0107 o wiadomo\u015b\u0107, od osoby kt\u00f3ra budowa\u0142a ten dom? Mo\u017ce ma kto\u015b zdj\u0119cia, jak wygl\u0105da dom w rzeczywisto\u015bci?\r\njmichalek1106@gmail.com","create_date":"2024-08-14 12:48:01","modify_date":"2024-08-14 12:48:01","status":"published","is_moderated":0,"attachments":[],"_uid":2589231},"entity_changes":false}
