2024-08-22 16:15:43 - StudioAtrium\Entity\Discuss\Post:Insert {"timestamp":1724343343,"user_id":null,"user_ip":"166.88.64.207","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 12_5) AppleWebKit\/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome\/114.0.0.0 Safari\/537.36 OPR\/89.0.4447.51","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post","entity_data":{"id":10134,"__foreign_props":[],"parent_id":"0","cat_id":"100","project_id":"1579","nick":"Jason","topic":"Boost Your Leads with Simple Tweaks","content":"Hey there, I'm Jason. I just stumpled upon your website and noticed a few areas where minor tweaks could increase your a lot more leads. I've helped several clients in your industry improve their websites, and they've seen a significant growth in leads due to these changes.\r\n\r\nI'm happy to jump on a quick call to discuss these improvements with you. I can fit you in this week, so at no cost, just to help.\r\n\r\nPlease tell me the best way to reach you, and we can schedule a time that works for you. These are straightforward changes and shouldn't take too long to fix.\r\n\r\nWarm Regards,\r\n\r\nJason Clemens\r\n** Visit: https:\/\/bit.ly\/FreeWebsiteAuditByJason\r\nOr reply to this email Jason.clemens01@gmail.com or call me at: +1-651-419-8101","create_date":"2024-08-22 16:15:43","modify_date":"2024-08-22 16:15:43","status":"published","is_moderated":0,"attachments":[],"_uid":2594351},"entity_changes":false}
